snippet.title: Amber alert GLMM/GLMV || Emotional Mini movie || Read desc for story explanation-
snippet.description:
Henlo :D
I hope you enjoyed this short GLMM/GLMV ❤️ 
I’m so sorry if its bad I’m a beginner I’m not a professional yet ;(

Here’s an explanation:
~~~
There are 2 siblings, One named “Maddie” (The oldest one with a hair down) that is 11 years old and “Kenzie” (The short one with tied hair) That is 9 years old.

They went to the park, Before they go in, Kenzie told her sister that she loves her and she’ll always be in her side no matter what. Maddie told her sister to promise that shell never leave her, she promised.

When they went in, the played allot of games, they got a little bored so they have decided to play hide and seek, Maddie wasn’t feeling good about it but she went with it. Kenzie looked for places to hide but she didn’t find a good spot, she went far from her sister, But she didn’t know where she was heading.

Kenzie went to an unknown place, she saw a k!dnapper with a dead body, when the k!dnapper saw Kenzie she ran to catch her. 

Maddie was done counting and went to search for Kenzie but unfortunately she didn’t find her anywhere. She went to her parents and told them about Kenzie. 
Mean while with Kenzie, the k!dnapper took her and tried to put her in a chair and tie her up, but Kenzie kept making it difficult by moving the chair. When Kenzie got hurt in her feet the k!dnapper turned her and sat her down then tied her up.

Maddie was in a search for Kenzie with her parents, she started to have flashback about the sweet moments of Kenzie, she started to be emotional because she realized that someone is really on her side and loved her. 

The k!dnapper decided to call her friends for backup, she didn’t want to murder a 9 year old. Maddie was still searching.

When the k!dnapper’s friends came, she asked what to do with Kenzie, her friend brought poisonous pills with her, they all agreed to poison her.

Her friend held her and opened Kenzie’s mouth so they can put the pill on her mouth, Kenzie accidentally swallowed it and became dizzy. Her friends heard footsteps and ran away. 

Maddie found Kenzie and she hugged her, she thought that Kenzie was alive... When Maddie raised her head she noticed that she was poisoned, Maddie got emotional and ran away she never looked back...
~~~
That’s it :DDD❤️
_______________________
